Voice Call => UDP => pode haver perda de pacotes => does not tolerate delay
Multimedia => UDP => Inelastico => need a minimum bandwidth
||
>>não precisa de todos os pacotes para funcionar na intrega

File transfer => TCP => precisa de todos os pacotes para um correto funcionamento 
elastico => use the bandwith that is available 





	SOCKETS

1=>Inter-process communication mechanism
2=>Client/server

	Identificação
	
1=>Family: AF_INET (IPv4), AF_INET6 (IPv6)
2=>Type: UDP(SOCK_DGRAM)
	 TCP(SOCK_STREAM)
	 RAW(SOCK_RAW)
3=>Address: local address (IP or path)
4=>Port: Local port 0-65535

5=>1 socket per Address, per Port, per Protocol, per Family, per Host

A Socket must be “Bound” to a local IP/PORT

bind()=>used to associate a Socket to a local IP/Port.
